dct_alternative_sm: Sacri Romani Imperii Circulus Rhenanus Superior
dct_description_sm: 2 bar scales on map, given in "Milliaria Germanica communia" and "Milliaria Gallica sive Horae itineris."
Latitudinal and longitudinal lines along margin.
Decorative cartouches (with coats of arms, cherubs), compass rose.
Descriptive text in lower right: Benevole Spectator!
Appears in Homann's Deutschland vor achtzehnhundertundeins.
